----------------------------------------------------

## How to Run the Project

* Step 1
Import project into Spring Tool Suite (STS)

* Step 2
Update Maven dependencies
Right Click Project → Maven → Update Project

* Step 3
Run application
Right Click RewardsApiApplication.java
→ Run As
→ Spring Boot App

* Step 4
Test API using browser or Postman
http://localhost:8080/api/rewards/101
